Title: 'The ultimate travel adventure with your heart as the guide '
DateModified: '2019-02-09'
DatePublished: '2019-02-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-ultimate-travel-adventure-with-your-heart-as-the-guide
SetInCountry: Mexico
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Ian Lyford
AuthorCountry: Australia
Text: Let your heart take you on an exotic journey from Sydney Australia to San Diego
  California then on to the trolley bus down to san ysidro across the border in to
  Mexico then make your way down to Ensenada on the abc bus line from Tijuana then
  venture down to los Cabos grab a flight to Mexico City then grab a bus to beautiful
  orizaba veracruz then make your way to the port of Veracruz by bus then take plane
  back to Tijuana cross border to San Diego then on to Sydney AUSTRALIA.
